                    "body": "Will pyarrow 5.0.0 be released with this fix? It seems I'm unable to {{pip install pyarrow}} today, due to this issue. [Here's a separate write-up|https://github.com/python-poetry/poetry/issues/3627#issuecomment-884943058].",
